This is your new Play 2.0 application
=====================================

This file will be packaged with your application, when using `play dist`.


setting up eclim:
-----------------
start eclim and from vim use the command ProjectsList if the close all the unnecessary projects except the one which is needed to improve the performance.
'ProjectRefresh' command to reflect all the changes to vim

Trouble shooting:
-----------------
If eclipse/eclim complaining about errors, which should not be, its better to clean compile. Command for the same is as follows:(on play console)
	'clean compile'

Configuring database
--------------------
in play console run the following command:
h2-browser   , user name and password will be same as that of mentioned in the application.conf.
